                                <p><strong>Click to upload image</strong></p>
                                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666;">JPG, PNG, GIF ‚Ä¢ Max 5MB ‚Ä¢ Saved to
                                    /uploads/ads/YYYY/MM/</p>
                            </div>
                            <img id="imagePreview"
                                style="max-width: 100%; max-height: 200px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 15px; display: none;">
