            </h2>

            <div
                style="background: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                <h4 style="color: #856404; margin-bottom: 10px;"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> How to use:</h4>
                <ol style="color: #856404; margin-left: 20px; font-size: 14px;">
                    <li><strong>Drag & drop</strong> multiple images OR click to select</li>
                    <li>Fill <strong>common settings</strong> (URL, position, etc.)</li>
                    <li><strong>Optional:</strong> Download CSV template ‚Üí Fill titles ‚Üí Upload with images</li>
                    <li>Click <strong>Bulk Upload</strong> ‚Üí All ads processed with optimization!</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 30px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                <!-- Bulk Image Upload -->
                <div>
                    <label style="display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #cc3366;">
                        <i class="fas fa-images"></i> Select Multiple Images
                    </label>
                    <div id="bulkDropZone" class="bulk-upload-zone">
                        <input type="file" id="bulkImages" name="images" multiple accept="image/*"
                            style="display: none;">
                        <i class="fas fa-cloud-upload-alt fa-4x" style="color: #cc3366;"></i>
                        <p style="margin: 15px 0 5px 0; font-weight: 600;">Drag & drop images here</p>
                        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">or <strong>click to browse</strong></p>
                        <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 10px;">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Max 50 images ‚Ä¢ 10MB each
                        </p>
                    </div>
